snippet.title: EGG in HOT OIL | Fried Eggs Recipe Cooking Village | Egg Fried in Oil | Fried Egg Puffs Recipe
snippet.description:
Today, in our village, we are cooking a delicious egg recipe with hot oil. First, we add eggs directly into boiling oil. Then we made an egg puffs recipe with vegetables and fried eggs. Normally, puffs are made in the oven, but we make them without the oven.

Finally, we enjoyed this snack recipe with tea. Yummy!

Episode 4012: CCTV Shop Kaun Jayega?
--------------------------------------------------------
Bhide arrives at the soda shop, only to discover it empty. When he questions everyone about their absence, they lie to him. Tapu Sena reveals Madhavi's scam ordeal, which Bhide was unaware of. Later, Jethalal and Iyer decide to pose as police officers to aid in apprehending the scammer at the CCTV shop.

About the show:

Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. snippet.title: Karishma Singh ने कान पकड़ कर मांगी सबके सामने Haseena से माफी | Maddam Sir | Hindi Comedy Show
snippet.description:
Karishma Singh ने कान पकड़ कर मांगी सबके सामने Haseena से माफी | Maddam Sir | Hindi Comedy Show


Show Synopsis : Four brave female police officers of Aminabad police station use their wittiness and emotional intelligence to tackle the various challenges they face at their work. The head of the pack is S.H.O Haseena Mallik, witty, romantic leads by example. The common challenge for all these women is to bring sensitivity to their policing while dealing with cases that come to this police station. Hence their solution are mostly unusual. The characters and the cases add to the fun and humour of the show. While Pushpa and Karishma are the saas bahu duo, who keep us entertained by their Squabbles, it is Haseena - Karishma's ideological differences which add to the drama and comedy.


Show Name : Maddam Sir
Star Cast: Kritika Kamra, Sharad Kelkar, Mohnish Behl, Rukhsar Rehman

snippet.description:

A tempo arrives to deliver a parcel as the members of the society are playing in the compound. Dr. Hathi surprised everyone by emerging from it dressed as an elephant. Everybody plays together all day long. Watch this fun-filled episode of Taarak Mehta Ka Oolta Chasmah.

Show Name - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast - Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt
Episode - 370
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi, Neela Asit Modi

#taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah #livcomedy #tmkoc #comedy2024 #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #comedy #jethalal #tarakmehta 
 
About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal’s Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance as he finds a philosopher in him. The housing society residents help each other find solutions when facing common, real-life challenges and getting involved in sticky situations.

Meet Chanchal, your everyday girl next door, whose life takes an unexpected turn when she gets possessed by the Korean Drama Ka Bhoot!

Boost your career, travel with confidence, and connect with new cultures. Download Duolingo and open doors to the world! https://app.adjust.net.in/19xp9iob 

In a desperate attempt to bring Chanchal back to reality, Sohan decides to seek professional help and takes her to an exorcist. Will they succeed in exorcising the K-Drama Ka Bhoot from Chanchal's life, or will the ghostly obsession take over everyone around her?

#TVF #KDrama #AhsaasChanna

snippet.title: Characters of Gaami - Teaser | Vishwak Sen | Chandini Chowdary | Vidyadhar Kagita | UV Creations
snippet.description:
#Gaami chronicles the adventurous journey of Shankar- a wounded, reluctant, and reclusive Aghora on his quest to find the cure for his very rare condition- ‘an inability to experience any human touch’.  But this adventure for cure would be fulfilled, only when he can confront and conquer his destiny that becomes intertwined with two other characters.

#GaamiTeaser #GaamiMovie #VishwakSen #ChandiniChowdary #VidyadharKagita #MGAbhinaya #MohammadSamad #NareshKumaran #GaamiTeluguMovie

snippet.description:
Be The First To Watch All Videos. Download the CurlyTales App: https://curlytale.page.link/DwNd

Our excitement knows no bounds as we host our dream guest, the iconic Sushmita Sen! Join us on this culinary and conversational journey as we explore Sushmita's love for Bengali maach, misti doi, and sondesh, while also uncovering her newfound passion for sushi. The air is filled with laughter and nostalgia as she fondly recalls the time she won Miss Universe, sharing entertaining stories and offering us a glimpse into her world. Brace yourselves for some etiquette tips straight from the graceful queen herself, adding a touch of elegance to our delightful brunch!

In this candid conversation, Sushmita also opens up about her experience reprising the iconic role in Aarya, the challenges faced, and the creative process behind the series' finale on Disney+hotstar

As we indulge in delectable sushi and dimsums, the conversation takes a meaningful turn towards the importance of health and self-love. Sushmita Sen, with her wisdom, guides us through the journey of prioritizing well-being. As the brunch unfolds, Sushmita's aura leaves us awestruck, a testament to the timeless charm and grace that defines her. 

Hit play now and immerse yourself in this unforgettable Sunday Brunch experience with Sushmita Sen. It's a rendezvous filled with laughter, delicious bites, heartwarming stories, and a touch of glamour, making it a brunch to remember. Don't miss the magic – join us for an extraordinary time with the incredible Sushmita Sen! 🌟

snippet.title: Aham ne Gopi ko kiya taiyaar! | Saath Nibhana Saathiya
snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe *Star Plus* : https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC-LPIU24bQXVljUXivKEeRQ

About* 
------------

               Yeh kahani hai ek sanyukt parivaar mai rehnewale Modi khaandaan ki. Izzatdaar, ameer aur naamcheen hone ke bawajud, ghar ke sanskaar aur sanskriti hain inka saccha dhan. Ghaata Episode 44 [Eng Sub] - Adeel Chaudhry - Momina Iqbal - Mirza Zain Baig - 20th February 2024 - Har Pal Geo

Hamza and Rania are deeply in love, a fact known to the entire family. Yet, unbeknownst to them, their cousins Danish and Sana secretly harbor affection for the couple.
A tragic event turns Rania’s life upside down and has major consequences for her relationship with Hamza. Danish and Sana, motivated by their hidden malice, use the event to their advantage.
As the aftermath unfolds, the four cousins experience the hardships of love, betrayal, and suffering. Boundaries are crossed, and each of them battles personal demons in their pursuit of love.
Will Rania and Hamza manage to be together? Can Rania overcome the haunting consequences of the event, or will it define her life? Will Hamza stand by Rania during the most testing time of her life? And will Danish and Sana confess their feelings to Rania and Hamza, respectively?

Ghaata Episode 44 [Eng Sub] - Adeel Chaudhry - Momina Iqbal - Mirza Zain Baig - 20th February 2024 - Har Pal Geo

Hamza and Rania are deeply in love, a fact known to the entire family. Yet, unbeknownst to them, their cousins Danish and Sana secretly harbor affection for the couple.
A tragic event turns Rania’s life upside down and has major consequences for her relationship with Hamza. Danish and Sana, motivated by their hidden malice, use the event to their advantage.
As the aftermath unfolds, the four cousins experience the hardships of love, betrayal, and suffering. Boundaries are crossed, and each of them battles personal demons in their pursuit of love.
Will Rania and Hamza manage to be together? Can Rania overcome the haunting consequences of the event, or will it define her life? Will Hamza stand by Rania during the most testing time of her life? And will Danish and Sana confess their feelings to Rania and Hamza, respectively?

7th Sky Entertainment Presentation

Shiddat Episode 03 [Eng Sub] - Muneeb Butt - Anmol Baloch - Digitally Presented by PEL - 19th February 2024 - HAR PAL GEO

Shiddat Digitally Presented by PEL

Asra, a beautiful and cherished young woman, has led a life filled with love and care from her family. In contrast, Sultan, a determined and charismatic perfectionist, overcomes the challenges of his troubled childhood to consistently achieve his desires.

Despite their stark personality differences, Asra falls in love with Sultan. However, after they marry, Asra realizes that Sultan is not the ideal man she had envisioned. To please him, she sacrifices her desires and undergoes a significant transformation.

This revelation becomes the catalyst for an unending series of problems between them. The journey through marital life becomes a complex maze as Asra and Sultan attempt to navigate challenges, each trying to mold the other according to their own will and preference.

Will Asra and Sultan change for each other, or will the growing list of problems between them persist? When Asra discovers the reality about Sultan, how will she react? Is Sultan contemplating leaving Asra? Can love overcome all obstacles, or are some differences too profound to bridge?
